### Cadastrar usuário
POST http://localhost:8080/usuarios
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Misael Dutra",
  "email": "misael@gmail.com",
  "senha": "01"
}


### Listar usuários
GET http://localhost:8080/usuarios


### Atualizar usuário
PUT http://localhost:8080/usuarios/4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome": "Misael",
  "email": "jonatasnovo@email.com",
  "senha": "4"
}


### Deletar usuário
DELETE http://localhost:8080/usuarios/2